      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i just sit here in the chair and look at my kids and i feel so terrible. they're always rushing around, working, taking care of my doctors and my meds... and i'm just sitting here getting slower and more difficult every single day. i feel like i'm just a weight around their necks.",
