    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just wish there was a way to make it stop being so hard for them. it feels so selfish to keep hanging on when i know i'm just making their lives harder and more expensive and stressful. sometimes i wonder if it would be okay to just... stop. you know? if i weren't here, they could finally breathe, and they could have their lives back. is that such an awful thought to have?",
